export const FormInstall = ({sty}) => {
  return (
    <FormikProvider value={formik}>
      <Form>
        <Flex vertical style={{ justifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center', textAlign: 'center' }}>
          <Title level={3} style={{ color: primaryColor }}>Fill the form to ask about anything you want</Title>
          <Row gutter={[16, 16]} style={{ width: '80%', marginTop: 24 }}>
            <Col span={12}>
              <InputFormik
                name="name"
                label="Name"
                variant="filled"
                aria-label="name"
                placeholder="Your Name"
              />
            </Col>
            <Col span={12}>
              <InputFormik
                name="email"
                variant="filled"
                label="Email"
                type="email"
                aria-label="email"
                placeholder="Your Email"
              />
            </Col>
            <Col span={24}>
              <InputFormik.TextArea
                name="message"
                variant="filled"
                label="Message"
                aria-label="message"
                placeholder="Your Message"
              />
            </Col>
          </Row>
        </Flex>
      </Form>
    </FormikProvider>
  );
}
